<span id="freeTextContainer17737338367977044541">Loved it! This history not only covers the use of spices in cuisine and medicine, but also in death rituals, religion, and as an aphrodisiac...as well as their decline, rise, decline, rise, decline, rise, decline, and rise...and decline. If you are interested in history in general, I would highly recommend this book. And, if you&apos;re anything like me, you will definitely want to try many of these old and ancient spiced sauces, beverages, and desserts.</span>
  <span id="freeText17737338367977044541" style="display:none">Loved it! This history not only covers the use of spices in cuisine and medicine, but also in death rituals, religion, and as an aphrodisiac...as well as their decline, rise, decline, rise, decline, rise, decline, and rise...and decline. If you are interested in history in general, I would highly recommend this book. And, if you're anything like me, you will definitely want to try many of these old and ancient spiced sauces, beverages, and desserts.</span>
